WEBVTT

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:11.419
Now if you just take a look at today's text, it says, come and witness the activities of

00:00:11.419 --> 00:00:15.279
Jehovah, witness.

00:00:15.279 --> 00:00:22.300
Now according to a dictionary, a witness is someone who has personal knowledge of something.

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:26.579
So how can we be witnesses of Jehovah?

00:00:26.579 --> 00:00:31.699
What personal knowledge do we have of his activities?

00:00:31.699 --> 00:00:38.219
Well, first of all, we can testify to the fact that Jehovah can see into the future.

00:00:38.219 --> 00:00:42.060
