00:02:11.580 --> 00:02:17.060
Daniel chapter 9 and verse 26.

00:02:17.060 --> 00:02:26.780
So now what's our objective here is to see that Jerusalem and its temple would be destroyed

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:30.219
a second time and the true worship would not last.

